name: Jumpy Dot Win
description: I, @mathmakesart, have beaten @mrdoob's "Jumpy Dot" NFT Game (OBJKT#7577) for the first time on 2021/03/21 at 20:57 GMT. My winning score is 8591. I previously claimed to be the world-record holder for this game, and having beaten it for the first time I am immortalizing this moment as an NFT.
